程序包 org.springframework.ui

Generic support for UI layer concepts.

请参阅: 说明

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    Model
    Java-5-specific interface that defines a holder for model attributes.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    ConcurrentModel
    Implementation of Model based on a ConcurrentHashMap for use in concurrent scenarios.
    ExtendedModelMap
    Subclass of ModelMap that implements the Model interface.
    ModelMap
    Implementation of Map for use when building model data for use with UI tools.

程序包org.springframework.ui的说明

Generic support for UI layer concepts. Provides a generic ModelMap for model holding.
